#: applications/luci-app-lxc/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/lxc/overview.js:454
msgid ""
"<b>Please note:</b> LXC Containers require features not available on OpenWrt "
"images for devices with small flash."
msgstr ""
"<b>ໝາຍເຫດ:</b> ຄອນເທນເນີ LXC ຕ້ອງການຄຸນສົມບັດທີ່ບໍ່ມີຢູ່ໃນອິມເມດ OpenWrt ສຳລັບອຸປະກອນທີ່ມີໜ່ວຍຄວ"
"າມຈຳແຟຣດນ້ອຍ."

